what: Axe, IBM, WAVE, and 10 custom tests

acts.what: used for tests on which chromium fails on some URLs
conduct and report an Axe test

items.description: Ensures all ARIA attributes have valid values
Ensures every id attribute value is unique

must pass any of.description: Document has multiple static elements with the same id attribute: personalized id

items.description: Landmarks should have a unique role or role/label/title (i.e. accessible name) combination

must pass any of.description: The landmark must have a unique aria-label, aria-labelledby, or title to make landmarks distinguishable

items.description: Ensures <meta name="viewport"> does not disable text scaling and zooming

must pass any of.description: user-scalable=no on <meta> tag disables zooming on mobile devices

acts.what: report the count of visible elements
tabulate and list focusable elements with and without focus outlines
tabulate and list visible focusable and operable elements
tabulate and list hover-caused context additions
tabulate and describe inconsistencies in labeling
tabulate and list underlined and other inline links
tabulate and list radio buttons in and not in accessible fieldsets
conduct and report an IBM test

items.message: Page detected as HTML, but does not have a 'lang' attribute
The page does not provide a way to quickly navigate to the main content (ARIA "main" landmark or a skip link)
Content is not within a landmark element

acts.what: conduct and report a WAVE test
